# Trading policy source of truth

Canonical strategy document: `0_Developer_Source_Files/trade_policies.md`

When changing policy selection, sweep, insurance, or exported drafts:

1. Read `trade_policies.md` before editing policy code.
2. After sweep/export, run or verify `ingest/scripts/update_trade_policies_doc.py` (auto-wired in optimizer, export, human review).
3. Cite `trade_policies.md` in handoffs and code reviews.

Manual sync: `PYTHONPATH=ingest/scripts python3 ingest/scripts/update_trade_policies_doc.py`
